üá¨üáß English

This project demonstrates an asynchronous task management platform in Python using FastAPI, SQLite, and background workers.

Features
	‚Ä¢	Asynchronous REST API for creating and retrieving tasks
	‚Ä¢	Background workers to process tasks
	‚Ä¢	SQLite database for task storage
	‚Ä¢	Modular architecture for scalability
	‚Ä¢	Easy to extend with new task types

